5. View Table Data
SELECT * FROM EMP_INFO;

Q1. Employee details with salary > 25000 and gender Female
SELECT * FROM EMP_INFO WHERE SAL > 25000 AND GENDER = 'Female';

Q2. Employee details with salary between 30000 and 40000
Correct query:
SELECT * FROM EMP_INFO WHERE SAL > 30000 AND SAL < 40000;

Alternative (better method):
SELECT * FROM EMP_INFO WHERE SAL BETWEEN 30000 AND 40000;

Q3. Employees who joined after Dec 12, 2019 OR salary greater than 25000 SELECT * FROM EMP_INFO WHERE JDATE > '2019-12-12' OR SAL > 25000;

Q4. Employees with salary >25000 and gender Male OR salary >30000
SELECT * FROM EMP_INFO WHERE (SAL > 25000 AND GENDER = 'Male') OR SAL > 30000;

Q5. Employees who have NOT joined on Oct 22, 2022
SELECT * FROM EMP_INFO WHERE NOT JDATE = '2022-10-22';

Alternative:
SELECT * FROM EMP_INFO WHERE JDATE <> '2022-10-22';



